101
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:51,470
♪White smiles and fireworks flare♪

102
00:06:52,060 --> 00:06:54,810
♪You're my precious gift♪

103
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:56,890
♪My whole life's shift♪

104
00:07:02,290 --> 00:07:04,120
