110
00:07:16,500 --> 00:07:17,910
It's Shi's child.

111
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:20,930
[Ultrasound Report]

112
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,080
How many months?

113
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,540
Two and a half.

114
00:07:29,370 --> 00:07:30,700
You know what you need to do,

115
00:07:30,790 --> 00:07:32,080
I suppose?

116
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:34,370
