126
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:53,040
So, Ms. Su,
you're here to claim my position?

127
00:07:53,290 --> 00:07:54,330
Whether he loves me or not,

128
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:56,450
I'm Mrs. Sheng,

129
00:07:56,870 --> 00:07:58,290
and I won't

130
00:07:58,450 --> 00:07:59,450
let anyone

131
00:07:59,450 --> 00:08:00,830
