132
00:08:10,540 --> 00:08:11,660
Gu Lanshan!

133
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,080
Alright.

134
00:08:16,790 --> 00:08:17,830
Who's got spades?

135
00:08:21,790 --> 00:08:23,410
Truth or Dare?

136
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,120
Truth.

137
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:32,080
Shwenny,

138
00:08:32,290 --> 00:08:33,750
