139
00:08:33,910 --> 00:08:35,830
En, you're going easy on him.

140
00:08:35,950 --> 00:08:37,000
There's nothing

141
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,330
Shi can't get.

142
00:08:42,330 --> 00:08:43,290
I'll do a dare.

143
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:46,080
So you do have things you can't get.

144
00:08:46,290 --> 00:08:47,700
Finally,

145
00:08:47,830 --> 00:08:49,250
