146
00:08:49,450 --> 00:08:50,080
Alright,

147
00:08:50,370 --> 00:08:51,370
how should we tease him?

148
00:08:51,540 --> 00:08:52,620
Shwenny,

149
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:55,370
say a romantic line to Shan,

150
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,700
with deep emotion.

151
00:08:58,620 --> 00:08:59,410
Good one.

152
00:08:59,580 --> 00:09:00,200
We always see you two

153
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,790
showing off your love.

154
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:02,700
Shwenny,

155
00:09:02,870 --> 00:09:04,160
