158
00:09:11,290 --> 00:09:12,080
Hurry.

159
00:09:13,830 --> 00:09:15,080
Shwenny has something to say.

160
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,160
Chu,

161
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:47,040
Nothing compares to you.

162
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,330
If I could,

163
00:09:50,700 --> 00:09:52,830
