168
00:10:13,540 --> 00:10:14,450
Where are you going?

169
00:10:14,580 --> 00:10:15,410
Let go.

170
00:10:16,950 --> 00:10:17,830
Why?

171
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:20,120
Can't act anymore?

172
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,750
Is it because of Han Chengchi?

173
00:10:24,540 --> 00:10:25,120
Let me tell you,

174
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:26,870
Han Chengchi's heart

175
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:29,330
