178
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:36,290
Stop deluding yourself

179
00:10:36,660 --> 00:10:38,910
and just be Mrs. Sheng.

180
00:10:48,620 --> 00:10:49,750
I'm pregnant.

181
00:10:50,540 --> 00:10:51,910
It's Shi's child.

182
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,100
[Ultrasound Report]

183
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,700
Mr. Sheng, a word of advice.

184
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:04,000
