188
00:11:09,930 --> 00:11:12,640
♪Memories hold tight♪

189
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:14,250
Remember your own rules.

190
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:15,750
I bit your lip,

191
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:16,910
