192
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:18,700
♪Time speeds away♪

193
00:11:18,700 --> 00:11:20,330
An illegitimate child?

194
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:21,660
What luck

195
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:23,370
running into Su Jiaojiao here.

196
00:11:23,450 --> 00:11:25,450
Yeah, I even got her autograph.

197
00:11:25,660 --> 00:11:26,870
I'm such a fan!

198
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:31,680
♪Your shadow fades to gray♪

199
00:11:31,890 --> 00:11:33,810
♪The warmth you left behind♪

200
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:38,720
[Infant Formula]

201
00:11:38,790 --> 00:11:40,830
Words have power.

202
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:43,540
Some can bring joy,

203
00:11:43,830 --> 00:11:44,870
