204
00:11:45,370 --> 00:11:46,830
and excitement,

205
00:11:48,450 --> 00:11:49,870
while others

206
00:11:50,410 --> 00:11:51,200
rip open wounds

207
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:53,040
