209
00:11:54,580 --> 00:11:58,180
♪Every heartbeat's thrill♪

210
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,200
You're pregnant.

211
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:01,000
How far along?

212
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:02,410
About

213
00:12:02,540 --> 00:12:03,790
