223
00:12:38,410 --> 00:12:39,500
How did you find out?

224
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:41,700
I've known you had feelings
for Han Chengchi.

225
00:12:42,410 --> 00:12:44,500
I married you

226
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:45,500
to

227
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:48,700
end that fantasy.

228
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:53,000
You thought that was an accident?

229
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,790
I used to dream

230
00:13:05,870 --> 00:13:07,750
of a simple, beautiful love,

231
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:10,910
but reality shattered that.

232
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:14,120
The people I cared about

233
00:13:14,790 --> 00:13:16,830
hurt and betrayed me.

234
00:13:17,620 --> 00:13:18,870
Now, I know,

235
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:21,410
a marriage without love

236
00:13:21,700 --> 00:13:23,040
is just an illusion.

237
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:35,750
Shi.

238
00:13:35,870 --> 00:13:37,370
What did you say to my wife?

239
00:13:38,870 --> 00:13:40,250
I told her

240
00:13:41,040 --> 00:13:43,500
I'm pregnant with your child.

241
00:13:44,660 --> 00:13:46,410
You've got some nerve.

242
00:13:47,950 --> 00:13:49,660
Trying to mess with my wife

243
00:13:49,910 --> 00:13:51,160
and slander me?

244
00:13:51,410 --> 00:13:52,660
Did I ever touch you?

245
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,000
Shi,

246
00:13:54,620 --> 00:13:56,080
