247
00:13:56,290 --> 00:13:57,830
You like me, and I like you.

248
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,040
Why stay with her

249
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:00,330
when there's no love?

250
00:14:00,500 --> 00:14:02,700
She's the only one I've ever loved.

251
00:14:03,450 --> 00:14:04,410
I'm telling you,

252
00:14:04,700 --> 00:14:06,080
I don't want to see you again.

253
00:14:06,250 --> 00:14:07,250
Got it?

254
00:14:32,890 --> 00:14:34,810
[Xia Fanhua]

255
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:36,830
Fanhua,

256
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:38,660
