259
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:41,790
Got it.

260
00:14:42,560 --> 00:14:44,640
[Huan]

261
00:14:45,250 --> 00:14:46,000
Huan,

262
00:14:46,330 --> 00:14:47,120
has Chu come back?

263
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:47,830
Yeah,

264
00:14:47,950 --> 00:14:49,540
- she just got home.
- She's home?

265
00:14:51,580 --> 00:14:52,540
Okay, thanks.

266
00:15:09,790 --> 00:15:10,790
Is everything handled?

267
00:15:10,950 --> 00:15:11,750
It's done.

268
00:15:12,410 --> 00:15:13,540
After tonight,

269
00:15:13,750 --> 00:15:14,830
she'll be tied

270
00:15:14,830 --> 00:15:16,080
to that Wang guy.

271
00:15:16,160 --> 00:15:16,910
But Auntie,

272
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,330
are you sure about

273
00:15:18,330 --> 00:15:19,950
marrying Gu Lanshan to him?

274
00:15:20,250 --> 00:15:20,870
I heard

275
00:15:20,870 --> 00:15:23,080
he's already buried three wives.

276
00:15:23,450 --> 00:15:24,580
What choice do I have?

277
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:26,910
I wanted her to marry
into the Xia family,

278
00:15:27,370 --> 00:15:29,000
but they fell apart.

279
00:15:29,290 --> 00:15:30,250
The Wang family

280
00:15:30,450 --> 00:15:31,620
promised to invest

281
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,250
if she marries him.

282
00:15:46,580 --> 00:15:48,370
Why did you get rid of our child?

283
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:55,290
I've been too easy on you.

284
00:15:55,620 --> 00:15:57,370
You only married me for your brother.

285
00:15:57,500 --> 00:15:58,330
Fine.

286
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:01,200
From now on,

287
00:16:01,450 --> 00:16:02,910
you pay his medical bills.

288
00:16:04,870 --> 00:16:06,080
You promised to save my brother,

289
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,750
that's why I married you.

290
00:16:07,870 --> 00:16:09,370
You begged me,

291
00:16:09,370 --> 00:16:10,120
and I saved him.

292
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,750
We're even.

293
00:16:11,950 --> 00:16:13,660
But if you need money,

294
00:16:13,660 --> 00:16:15,330
I've got ways for you to earn it.

